    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The engine currently has a blown head gasket and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the wheel arches and a large dent on the rear passenger door. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This is an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or as a source for spare parts.",
